title: Tete Montoliu, Niels-Henning Orsted Pedersen - 1982 - Face To Fa
description:
Tete Montoliu, Niels-Henning Orsted Pedersen - 1982 - Face To Face

The two masters have recorded before on well known albums like, Tete, Tete a Tete, Words of Love, Catalonian Fire and Tootie's Tempo. Tete Montoliu spent most of his career recording for various European-based record labels, with some of his best works appearing on Steeplechase. Such as this duo live session with bassist Niels Pedersen. Montoliu chose his collaborator well, because he responds wonderfully to an aggressive pianist like Tete, providing strong support and lively interplay without stepping on him. The program is dominated by standards, (no originals this time) all of them well developed between 9 and 11 minutes each.

Track list:
01 - There'll Never Be Another You
02 - I Love You
03 - I Fall In Love Too Easily
04 - Lover Man & Salt Peanuts

Enjoy and share!
